														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1534182">
									

<p>Not a silly question in the least. The old man, even in his current state, is still a man driven by fear- he's too afraid to use the sack's final use on anything other than the third brother because if it doesn't work, he's just lost his last chance. It might very well be that the sack could have been used in a better manner, but the old man won't because he's still too afraid to do so. Besides, the things trapped in the sack might still be inside, and they won't be at all happy to see him.</p>

							</div>

								
					
